RogueStar Animation and Graphics Library

StatefulArrow - inspired by the YAMPA arrow, an arrow transformer that allows an arrow to 
                self-modify when iterated over itself.

SwitchedArrow - (unimplemented) an arrow transformer that implements switching

ThreadedArrow - (unimplemented) an arrow transformer that implements threading
                each thread has the ability to spawn a thread or die

TestFunctions - some quick and dirty sanity tests, load this up in ghci
